h2. üè∑Ô∏è Labeling & Categorization Best Practices

h3. Essential Labels
| **Category** | **Labels** | **Purpose** |
|---|---|---|
| **Priority** | critical, high-priority, low-priority | Impact urgency |
| **Type** | bug, feature, enhancement, technical-debt | Work classification |
| **Domain** | frontend, backend, database, api, security | Technical area |
| **Team** | team-alpha, team-beta, cross-team | Ownership |
| **Status** | blocked, needs-review, ready-for-qa | Work state |
| **Customer** | customer-facing, internal-tool | Impact scope |

h3. Component Assignment
* **Frontend**: UI/UX changes, client-side logic
* **Backend**: Server-side logic, business rules  
* **Database**: Schema changes, data migrations
* **API**: Integration points, service interfaces
* **Security**: Authentication, authorization, compliance
* **DevOps**: Infrastructure, deployment, monitoring

